                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4271" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1063</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13131 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">壹号土猪：北大猪肉大王的生意经</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yihao Organic Pork：Business Expertise of Pork King of Peking University</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朱沆，曾兢，冯瑞婷</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中山大学管理学院</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">壹号食品</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">壹号土猪；品牌；全产业链；2019百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yihao Organic Pork; Brand; Whole Industry Chain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">不安分的北大毕业生陈生意外发现容量巨大的猪肉市场却没有一个好品牌，而且消费能力与供应质量倒挂，雄心勃勃的陈生果断决定进入猪肉市场，一心想让人们看到北大毕业生能把卖猪肉做成大事业。2007年，陈生率领团队打造的高端土猪肉品牌——壹号土猪正式登陆市场，以创新的推广方式和一系列的事件营销持续引爆市场。壹号土猪的成功也引发行业内外众多经营者的模仿与跟进。在激烈的竞争中，壹号土猪不断在上下游的经营模式上进行探索，逐渐摸索出一套行之有效的全产业链经营模式。几年的淘汰赛下来，不少眼热土猪肉市场的竞争者亏损出局，壹号土猪的品牌知名度、销售网点和营业收入却年年提升，陈生成了名副其实的土猪大王。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Chen Sheng, an ambitious graduate of Peking University, accidentally found that there lacks a good brand in the pork market where not only has huge market volume but also existed the inversion between consumption power and supply quality. The aspirant Chen Sheng decided to come onto the pork market, hoping to let people know that graduate of Peking University can also make pork selling become a big business. In 2007, Chen Sheng led his team to build a high-end organic pork brand – Yihao Organic Pork officially appeared in the market, which exploded the market with innovative promotion methods and continuous event marketing. The success of the Yihao Organic Pork also triggered the imitation and follow-up of numerous business operators inside and outside the industry. During the fierce competition, Yihao Organic Pork continues to explore the management modes of upstream and downstream, and gradually explores a set of effective management modes of the whole industry chain. After several years of elimination, many competitors who are envious of organic pork market withdrew from the market with deficit. The popularity of the brand, sales outlets and business income of Yihao Organic Pork has increased year by year. Chen sheng is true to the name “king of the organic pork”.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业纵向边界 品牌管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-12</td>
                            </tr>
